{"tid":1895860,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣巴打上","createTime":"2020-02-24T19:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T03:20:38.000Z","uid":344352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"001bbb34360bfc0a4eb61060a9dd30533bbc6563","tid":1895860,"uid":344352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T19:33:39.000Z","msg":"我知道每位文宣手足都好努力好努力咁做緊文宣<br />\n我都係<br />\n雖則話要做文宣，但總會有漏氣嘅時候<br />\n會諗點解整左成個鐘嘅圖得10幾個人睇<br />\n做文宣會氣餒，但唔好放棄<br />\n我地同班仆街正苦鬥長命<br />\n一定勁過套「珍惜香港這個家」廣告<br />\n知文宣巴打絲打辛苦<br />\n所以整左張圖比大家笑下挽下<br />\n笑完就繼續努力，做出更好嘅文宣<br />\n好人一世平安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Re865d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRe865d4.png&h=a1b2df4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3528815a3085c5c5d35ffbe9f6ea040ac429a52","tid":1895860,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T19:35:06.000Z","msg":"我有睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6d7de92cbdda73bd0b09483e45f408f0ccaf6b","tid":1895860,"uid":324380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T19:45:17.000Z","msg":"我都有睇架，好多做得好好，多謝文宣巴打。加油呀！💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻"},{"pid":"0f5a2916e880397d4c83bf0adfac8bcb2e825825","tid":1895860,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T20:51:20.000Z","msg":"有睇，我條邨既老人家都有睇。<br />\n<br />\n但要承認近排真係令人好灰心"},{"pid":"d97f4311ec65f00955638462800e59f294d650c0","tid":1895860,"uid":344352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:18:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38da7e1bb686ebdbd0f74b664ec2694ce721bb53","tid":1895860,"uid":344352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28bc5476ae0557d3bc921c6e903925405035d85f","tid":1895860,"uid":344352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T03:19:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bad386b8cc2432304c22af534cc9ddbdc239f993","tid":1895860,"uid":344352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor